58
00:08:28.870 --> 00:08:32.890
And his book. oh. dear me. it had some
wicked spells in it.

59
00:09:10.950 --> 00:09:11.950
Monster.

60
00:09:13.080 --> 00:09:15.190
Oh. la. oh.

61
00:09:22.850 --> 00:09:25.270
Les dames amants. les dames amies.

62
00:09:36.690 --> 00:09:38.710
Les mega cutas.

63
